ovascular concerns, as it may be associated with certain cardiovascular risk factors.\"}, {\"title\": \"Nutritional Value\", \"description\": \"While chickpea flour and nuts (almond, pistachio) are present and could offer some protein and fiber, their contribution might be outweighed by the higher amounts of sugar, refined flour, and saturated fat. The product\'s overall nutritional density might be limited given its composition as a sweet confection.\"}, {\"title\": \"Processing Level\", \"description\": \"This product contains refined wheat flour and significant amounts of sugar, indicating it is likely a highly processed food. Foods high in refined grains and added sugars are often considered less ideal for a balanced diet, especially for individuals with blood sugar and cardiovascular conditions.\"}], \"guidance\": [\"You may want to consider consuming this product in very small, controlled portions to help manage sugar and saturated fat intake.\", \"It could be helpful to monitor your blood sugar levels closely if you choose to consume this product, to observe any potential effects.\", \"You may want to explore alternative sweet options that are lower in added sugars, refined grains, and saturated fats, and higher in fiber.\", \"Consider balancing any consumption of this product with a diet rich in whole foods, lean proteins, and plenty of vegetables and fruits to support overall health.\", \"Consulting with a healthcare professional or a registered dietitian could provide personalized advice regarding appropriate dietary choices for your specific health conditions.\"]}', '2026-03-22 11:13:22'),
(34, 6, 'Puffcorn', 'Kurkure', 55, 'MODERATE', '6_9f1d4d378f254e6b8958abe39d0a0171.jpg', 'Ask Gemini\njsL2blstSJv9aJwaqk3HajcA:1774235181797&udm=2&fbs=ADc_l-aNOCWEZBOHjofHoaMM...\nTANCES)\nCa\n(Pack Of 12)\nnetindia\nare Puffcorn-Yummy...\nTS: Roe Moel, Eds Shabie Of, Corn Meal.\ncs&Condiments on Powder, Chilli Powder,\nFondi Anmar Pouser Garlic Powder, Ginger\nFor Powder Emeric Powder, Spices Extract,\nSuger Black Salt Tomato Powder\nDentrout Mix Solds\nNATURAL & NATURE DENTICAL\nOpen Food Facts\nINGREDIENTS: Cereal Products (67%) (Corn Meal (53%), Rice Meal (14%)),\nEdible Vegetable Oil (Palmolein), *Seasoning (Sugar, lodised Salt,\nMaltodextrin, Spices and Condiments, Milk Solids, Cheese, Salt Replacer\n(Potassium Chloride), Flavour (Natural and Nature Identical Flavouring\nSubstances), Flavour Enhancers (627, 631), Acidity Regulators (296, 330),\nEmulsifying & Stabilising Agent ((331(iii), 471, 327)), Gram Meal (3.6%),\nCalcium Carbonate (170(i)), lodised Salt.\nAs flavouring agent. Contains Onion and Garlic\nALLERGEN ADVICE: Contains Soy, Milk, Wheat\nPuffcorn-Kurkure - 28 10rs\nImages may be subject to copyright Learn more\nShare\nSave\n3,210 x 1,309\nVisit >\n#days ago\nINGREENTS: C Meal (52.0 eVegetable\nBak Pepper\nMilk Solids Calum Carbonate (10)\nNanda Wholesale Mart\nMasala Munch - *5...', '{\"overall_score\": 55, \"risk_level\": \"MODERATE\", \"overview\": \"This product contains several ingredients that could potentially be a concern for individuals managing blood sugar and cardiovascular conditions. It includes refined cereal products, added sugars, and sources of saturated fat and sodium, which may not be ideal for these health profiles.\", \"sugar_estimate\": \"Medium\", \"additives_count\": 8, \"allergens_found\": [], \"ingredients\": [{\"ingredient_name\": \"Corn Meal\", \"status\": \"CAUTION\", \"reason\": \"As a refined cereal product, it may have a relatively high glycemic index, which could potentially contribute to fluctuations in blood sugar levels for individuals managing blood sugar conditions.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Rice Meal\", \"status\": \"CAUTION\", \"reason\": \"Similar to corn meal, refined rice meal might be associated with a higher glycemic response, potentially affecting blood sugar management for individuals with blood sugar conditions.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Edible Vegetable Oil (Palmolein)\", \"status\": \"CAUTION\", \"reason\": \"Palmolein is a form of palm oil, which contains saturated fats. While not as high as some other oils, a higher intake of saturated fats is generally associated with potentially affecting cardiovascular health in some individuals.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Sugar\", \"status\": \"CAUTION\", \"reason\": \"Added sugars could potentially contribute to an increase in blood sugar levels and may not be ideal for individuals managing blood sugar conditions. Higher sugar intake might also be a concern for cardiovascular health.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Iodised Salt\", \"status\": \"CAUTION\", \"reason\": \"High sodium intake is often linked to potentially contributing to elevated blood pressure, which could be a concern for individuals with cardiovascular conditions.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Maltodextrin\", \"status\": \"CAUTION\", \"reason\": \"This is a highly processed carbohydrate that may have a high glycemic index, potentially causing a rapid increase in blood sugar levels, which could be a concern for individuals with blood sugar conditions.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Spices and Condiments (Onion and Garlic)\", \"status\": \"SAFE\", \"reason\": \"Generally considered safe and may offer some beneficial compounds; specific spices could potentially affect individuals differently, but in general usage, they are usually not a major concern.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Milk Solids\", \"status\": \"SAFE\", \"reason\": \"Typically used as a flavor enhancer and texture agent. For a user with no specified dairy sensitivity, it is generally considered safe.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Cheese\", \"status\": \"SAFE\", \"reason\": \"Provides flavor and is generally considered safe for individuals without dairy sensitivities.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Salt Replacer (Potassium Chloride)\", \"status\": \"CAUTION\", \"reason\": \"While used to reduce sodium, a higher intake of potassium chloride could potentially be a concern for individuals with certain kidney conditions or those on specific medications. Consulting a healthcare professional regarding its intake might be advisable.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Flavour (Natural and Nature Identical Flavouring Substances)\", \"status\": \"SAFE\", \"reason\": \"These are generally used in small quantities to enhance taste and are often considered safe for consumption.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Flavour Enhancers (627, 631)\", \"status\": \"CAUTION\", \"reason\": \"These are often used in processed foods. Some individuals might experience sensitivities, and while generally recognized as safe, a higher intake of such additives in a diet could be a consideration for overall health.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Acidity Regulators (296, 330)\", \"status\": \"SAFE\", \"reason\": \"These are common food acids used in small quantities and are generally considered safe for consumption.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Emulsifying & Stabilising Agent (331(iii), 471, 327)\", \"status\": \"SAFE\", \"reason\": \"These are common food additives used to improve texture and stability and are generally considered safe for consumption in typical food quantities.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Gram Meal\", \"status\": \"SAFE\", \"reason\": \"Gram meal is generally considered a good source of protein and fiber, which could potentially be beneficial for blood sugar management and overall digestive health.\"}, {\"ingredient_name\": \"Calcium Carbonate (170(i))\", \"status\": \"SAFE\", \"reason\": \"This is a common calcium supplement and anti-caking agent, generally considered safe.\"}], \"risk_analysis\": [{\"title\": \"Blood Sugar Impact\", \"description\": \"The product contains refined carbohydrates such as corn meal, rice meal, sugar, and maltodextrin. These ingredients may contribute to a quicker rise in blood sugar levels, which could be a concern for individuals managing blood sugar conditions. Limiting intake of such items is generally considered a supportive approach for blood sugar management.\"}, {\"title\": \"Cardiovascular Considerations\", \"description\": \"Ingredients like palmolein (a source of saturated fat), added sugar, and iodised salt may not be ideal for cardiovascular health. Higher intake of saturated fats and sodium is often linked to potentially affecting blood pressure and overall heart health. The presence of a salt replacer (potassium chloride) might also warrant caution, especially for individuals with certain health conditions, and professional advice might be useful.\"}, {\"title\": \"Processing Level & Additives\", \"description\": \"This product appears to be highly processed, containing multiple E-numbers including flavour enhancers (627, 631), acidity regulators, and emulsifying agents. While many of these are generally recognized as safe in moderation, a diet consistently high in highly processed foods and additives might be a consideration for overall well-being, particularly for seniors.\"}, {\"title\": \"Nutritional Value\", \"description\": \"Primarily composed of refined cereal products, this snack might not offer a substantial amount of essential nutrients, fiber, or protein compared to whole, unprocessed foods. For seniors, choosing nutrient-dense options is often suggested to support overall health and specific dietary requirements.\"}], \"guidance\": [\"Consider consuming this product in very limited quantities due to its potential impact on blood sugar levels and cardiovascular health.\", \"You may want to focus on snacks that are lower in added sugars, refined carbohydrates, and sodium to help manage your blood sugar and cardiovascular well-being.\", \"Reading nutrition labels for total carbohydrates, sugars, sodium, and saturated fats could help you make more informed dietary choices.\", \"Consider consulting with a healthcare professional or a registered dietitian for personalized dietary advice tailored to your specific health needs and conditions.\"]}', '2026-03-23 03:08:38');
