(210, 23, 'Sugar', 'AVOID', 'Extremely high sugar content directly contributes to elevated blood sugar levels, worsening diabetes management. It also negatively impacts cardiovascular health by increasing risk factors like obesity, high triglycerides, and inflammation. This is highly detrimental for an individual with blood sugar and cardiovascular conditions.'),
(211, 23, 'Caramel Colour (E150d)', 'CAUTION', 'This specific caramel coloring (sulfite ammonia caramel) can contain 4-methylimidazole (4-MEI), a potential carcinogen. While consumption levels are key, it is an unnecessary additive and generally advisable to limit exposure, especially for seniors with existing health concerns.'),
